  "texts": [
    "LLMs represent an undeniably mega-trend in the current century in many fields and industrial sectors.",
    "In the particular case of learning, these generative AI-based solutions have produced a considerable buzz.",
    "Accordingly, they enable hands-on learning and are commonly used in classrooms nowadays.",
    "Compared to previous AI solutions and traditional methodologies, which focused primarily on modifying the textual input, advanced LLMs can generate onthe-fly human-like utterances, enhancing pedagogical practice and providing personalized assessment and tutoring.",
    "Given the popularity of LLMs, this work is the first to contribute with a comprehensive overview of their application within the educational field, paying particular attention to those that involved students or teachers in the design or experimental plan."
  ],
